OL,3,CBirmingham City Hospital officially
OL,4,Ccloses as final patient leaves
OL,6,FAfter 135 years of treating patients
OL,7,Fon site on Dudley Road, Birmingham
OL,8,FCity Hospital officially closed its
OL,9,Fdoors today.
OL,11,FWork began at 5am to move the
OL,12,Fremaining 110 patients over to the new
OL,13,FMidland Metropolitan University
OL,14,FHospital, just 1.7 miles away.
OL,16,FPatients were moved one-by-one by
OL,17,Fambulance with the final one leaving
OL,18,Fjust before midday.
