OL,3,CBirmingham City Hospital officially
OL,4,Ccloses as final patient leaves
OL,6,FThat patient was given a special
OL,7,Ffarewell as he is one of the
OL,8,Fhospital's own; Dr Pankaj Kumar has
OL,9,Fworked at the site as a Specialist A&E
OL,10,FDoctor for 18 years. A recent bout of
OL,11,Fpneumonia saw him admitted, and so
OL,12,Fcolleagues lined the corridors to wave
OL,13,Fhim off in a moment he clearly found
OL,14,Fvery moving.
OL,16,FToday's moving of patients from City
OL,17,Fto the new site, ends a month-long
OL,18,Fphased effort to move all the patients
OL,19,Ffrom City Hospital, and nearby
OL,20,FSandwell General, under one roof.
