OL,3,CBirmingham City Hospital officially
OL,4,Ccloses as final patient leaves
OL,6,FOnce patients were out of the
OL,7,Fhospital, staff gathered on the empty
OL,8,Fwards to mark an emotional moment,
OL,9,Fwhilst others had the more official
OL,10,Fjob of checking the whole site for any
OL,11,Fleftover medication or any items with
OL,12,Fpatient details on.
OL,14,FAny piece of equipment that can be
OL,15,Fused at the new site are being
OL,16,Fpackaged up to take over but move
