OL,6,FThe Birmingham and Midland Eye Centre
OL,7,Fand the Birmingham Treatment Service
OL,8,Fmean some medical services will stay
OL,9,Fon what will become known as the City
OL,10,FHealth Campus, but the old hospital
OL,11,Fwings will be knocked down and
OL,12,Freplaced with housing in the coming
OL,13,Fmonths.
